data.description: A perfect opportunity to own a corner unit Villa in the highly desired community of Riverwalk. This original Capri model is ready for your updating touches. A blank pallet awaits you. A brand new AC installed first week of April.  The backyard has room for a pool if you desire. The community amenities are extensive-to much to list. Villa is conveniently located in the Heart of Palm Beach County- airport, turnpike, I-95, entertainment just minutes from the community entrance gate. This villa is safely tucked away in this quiet community with a manned security gate and security patrol. Additional community information can be found at  website riverwalkofwpb, there you will find a wealth of information on what Riverwalk has to offer. Schedule a showing today.
